Tga '''Timzgid n Tinml''' nɣ '''Timzgid Taxatart n Tinml''' (illa daɣ mad as ittinin ''Tinmal'') yat tmzgid n tasuta tis-XII, tlla ɣ yat tmazirt ism as ɣd nttat Tinml, ɣ [[Adrar n Drn|Udrar n Drn]] ɣ [[Lmɣrib]]. Mqqar ɣ ass ad ur sul da tswuri am Timzgid, iɣrban nns suln ar ɣil ad gan inagan f umzruy nns imqqurn, tsul ar ɣil ad tga yan ɣ idɣarn imzrayn lli bahra ilan atig ɣ tmazirt. Tettyubna tmzgid ad ɣ udɣar lli ɣ ittumḍal Ibn Tumrt, amkras n umussu n [[Imwaḥḥidn|imuwaḥḥidn]]. Tga tmzgid ad yan umdya axatar f tmsdagt tamuwaḥḥidit.

== Amzruy ==
Tlla Tinml ɣ yat tizi taxatart n idrarn n Waṭlas mqqurn ad t igan d Tizi n Tst gr Mrrakc ɣ iẓẓlmḍ d tsga n Sus ɣ iffus. Tkka tt inn tga tamaẓunt tamzwarut n umussu [[Imwaḥḥidn|amuwaḥḥidi]] nna igan Ibn Tumrt amkras nns. Iṣku imḍfurn nns ɣid ɣ 1124 nɣ 1125, d ɣinn ad t inn ikkan iga tasila nna ɣ d ukʷin imrabṭn nna inbḍn tamazirt ɣ uzmz ann. Yat tmzgid tamzwarut  tettyubna ɣid ɣ uzmz ann nɣ imikk n tizi dffir. Lliɣ immut Ibn Tumrt ɣ 1130, ittumḍal ɣinn d skrn middn g umḍl nns zun d kra n ḍḍariḥ asgdan d adɣar n lḥajj ḍaṛt mayad. Ɛabd Al Mumin, lli d iɣʷin anbaḍ n [[Imwaḥḥidn|imuwaḥḥidn]] ḍaṛt tmttant n Ibn Tumrt, iqrrer ad ibnu yat tmzgid tamaynut ɣ tama nɣ iggi n udɣar ad ɣ 1148, mk lli s ittyara s usddid ɣ warratn iqburn n uzmz ann. Mqqar asakud n usadur n 1153- 1154 lli ifka Rawd Al Qirtas tsul ttubdar dar kigan. Timzgid tamaynut irwas is tumẓ adɣar n Timzgid lli illan
